opens its folded petals to absorb
the suns rays with its whole body.

Il prend cette forme lorsquil a fait le plein
de soleil. Il dborde alors dnergie et reste

Pendant sa priode de bourgeonnement,

After absorbing plenty of sunlight, Cherrim takes
this form. Its full of energy while its like this,
and its liveliness will go on until sundown.

As a bud, it barely moves. It sits still, placidly
waiting for sunlight to appear.

Les ptales de sa fleur panouie mettent
une odeur dlicate qui attire les Pokmon Insecte.

Lorsquil se ferme, ses ptales sont si durs quil
ne craint plus les attaques des Pokmon oiseaux.

Die Bltenbltter, die es umschlieen, sind hart.
Deswegen macht es ihm absolut nichts aus, wenn
Vogel-Pokmon es mit ihren Schnbeln angreifen.

Wenn es in voller Blte steht, strmt es einen
zarten Duft aus, der Kfer-Pokmon anlockt.

Al cerrarse, sus ptalos son tan duros que
resultan inmunes a los picotazos de los Pokmon
pjaro.

Cuando abre sus ptalos, libera una sutil
fragancia que atrae a los Pokmon insecto.

I petali ripiegati sono molto duri e lo proteggono
dalle beccate dei Pokmon alati.

Il profumo delicato emanato dai suoi petali
in piena fioritura attira i Pokmon di tipo
Coleottero.

Its folded petals are pretty tough. Bird Pokmon
can peck at them all they want, and Cherrim
wont be bothered at all.

The faint scent that emanates from its full
blossom entices bug Pokmon to it.
